author: Meg Teckman-Fullard and Kevin Reilly
title: Wuhan ended its 76-day coronavirus lockdown last week — here's how Wuhan residents are reacting
description: The government of Wuhan, China, last week ended a citywide lockdown that had brought the city to a standstill for 76 days. Wuhan was the city where the first known case of the coronavirus was reported in December 2019. Roads, train stations, and the city's ai…
content:
Getting back to normal is possibly in sight for the residents of Wuhan, China, the epicenter for the coronavirus outbreak.
